Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.54,0:00:06.98,Episode Title,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1)\c&H8255ea&}Let's {\c&H6badf3&}Play {\c&H78e2ad&}with the \N{\c&Hc59877&}Gymnastics {\c&H6badf3&}Club and {\c&H8255ea&}Musicals
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.92,0:00:05.58,Main Dialogue Top,Yume,0,0,0,,Charm girls, congratulations \Non your anime debut!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.58,0:00:06.98,Main Dialogue Top,All,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.98,0:00:08.08,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.08,0:00:09.95,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,How was your first anime adaptation?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.95,0:00:13.04,Main Dialogue,Haruna,0,0,0,,I was amazed to see us moving on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:17.34,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,I was worried my beauty would be lost \Nin the transition to anime form,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.34,0:00:18.86,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,but they did an acceptable job.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.86,0:00:21.75,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess there weren't any major problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:26.60,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,I just wonder if the people watching \Nbought that as a collaboration.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.60,0:00:29.92,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,I feel like we didn't really \Nhave much direct interaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:31.40,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.40,0:00:33.77,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,We sang together at the ending
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.77,0:00:37.13,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,and were able to do this club's \Nfamous ad-lib corner,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.13,0:00:39.18,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,so I think it felt like a real collaboration.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:41.72,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Well, it was good for a first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:44.69,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,And we were more comfortable with \Nslice-of-life than we thought, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:47.48,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,But will we be okay with five more \Nmembers suddenly coming in?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:51.86,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,With this many members every time, \Nwon't it be hard on the production staff?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:53.16,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.16,0:00:55.73,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,We already had the mob girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.73,0:00:58.45,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,so another five members won't \Nbe much added effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.45,0:00:59.20,Main Dialogue,Sonota,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.45,0:00:59.62,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:00.32,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.89,0:01:01.41,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.41,0:01:04.08,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Incidentally, how was the \Nad-lib part for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.08,0:01:06.58,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,It was my first time, so I can't really say yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:09.67,Main Dialogue,Haruna,0,0,0,,It's a unique format, so I was a little bewildered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:12.23,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,The scriptwriter just wants \Nto have it easy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.23,0:01:13.21,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,That's a terrible system.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.21,0:01:16.09,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,My character is laid-back,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:19.39,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,so it doesn't make a difference to me \Nwhether there's a script or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.39,0:01:22.22,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,I think I got a feeling for how tough \Nit's probably been up to now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.22,0:01:24.73,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,for the members of the Tesaguri Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.73,0:01:28.27,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Even for us, it took a little time before we could
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.27,0:01:29.98,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,loosen up and enjoy it like we do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:32.33,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Just keep at it and figure it out \Nthrough trial and error.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.33,0:01:32.98,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.98,0:01:35.56,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,But what'll we do during that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.56,0:01:36.68,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Good question...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.68,0:01:38.28,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Maybe for the Charm members,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:42.90,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,we should give a proper introduction \Nof {\i1}Tesagure! Bukatsumono.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.90,0:01:47.84,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,There are probably a lot of people who just \Nstarted watching with this Charm spin-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:49.42,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Then this'll be a highlight episode, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:53.46,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,But just a highlight episode would be boring, \Nso let's try doing it as a musical!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.46,0:01:54.94,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,M-Musical?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.94,0:01:55.92,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,That's new!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:01:59.18,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,So let's have another fun collaboration, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:00.97,Main Dialogue,All,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:35.99,Main Dialogue,N,0,0,0,,A summary of {\i1}Apprentice Goddesses \NPuru-Purun Charm{\i0} thus far.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.60,0:03:40.99,Main Dialogue,N,0,0,0,,The Apprentice Goddesses \Nrose up to save the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:44.56,Main Dialogue,N,0,0,0,,But actually, they were sitting in a java dive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.56,0:03:46.32,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Who says "java dive"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:47.79,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:51.65,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Doesn't the word "summary" remind you \Nof fish? Like, "summery" and "sinewy"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.65,0:03:53.05,Main Dialogue,Haruna,0,0,0,,I don't know about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:56.44,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,I want to become the goddess of liberty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:59.00,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,I think she's the most famous goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:00.38,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,I wanna be free!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:02.76,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,I think you act plenty free already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:05.50,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,That's not true. There are all \Nkinds of inconveniences!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:06.23,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,For example?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.23,0:04:08.69,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,For example, most Japanese \Ncan't tell the difference
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.69,0:04:11.45,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,between French and the Tsugaru dialect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:12.50,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Comprenez-vous?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:15.02,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,I don't understand Tsugaru dialect, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:19.62,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,That reminds me, Yua-senpai, \Nyou used to live in Poland, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:22.70,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,I've never heard you speak Polish before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:26.68,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Of course not. To be honest,\NI don't think I can speak it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:31.24,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Maybe that's already been \Nwiped from your backstory.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.24,0:04:33.00,Main Dialogue,Haruka/Aoi,0,0,0,,That's new!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:35.72,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,What kind of goddess do you \Nwant to be, Kanon-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:39.77,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,I would say a goddess of the arts, a muse!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.77,0:04:44.55,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Having mastered every known art form, \NI'll bet I already am a muse in a parallel world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:47.88,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,I can see it! I look at you \Nand think "entertainment"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:50.61,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,That image is of a comedian!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.61,0:04:52.50,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Hey, what about you, Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:54.78,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:04:57.65,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Well, you know we got a lot \Nof English homework today...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:59.93,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,I wondererd why you weren't \Njoining in our discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.93,0:05:04.91,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Well, it didn't sound like your \Nconversation was going anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:10.07,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,No! It's my fault for having nothing to add!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:15.17,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Hiina doesn't always \Nparticipate in our conversations, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.17,0:05:16.00,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:20.07,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Because your conversations \Nare always so unproductive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:22.52,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Either that, or I don't want to get burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:26.24,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,O-Our "Hina-san" really doesn't hold back, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:27.66,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,That's fresh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.54,0:05:29.68,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:32.19,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,What kind of goddess do \Nyou want to be, Yui-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:33.23,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:35.76,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,Good question...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:37.83,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,Ah! How about a goddess of victory?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:39.31,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,I like exercising, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:42.07,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,All muscle and no brain, as always...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.56,0:05:44.95,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say I have no aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:47.28,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,"No brain," not "no aim"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:49.72,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,Well, they're basically the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:51.43,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,No, they're not! And that hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:52.74,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,You're too carefree!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:55.83,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,What kind of goddess do you \Nwant to become, Hina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:57.42,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:06:01.92,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Sorry, I didn't give it any thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:05.34,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,And yet I called this topic unproductive...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:07.45,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,I don't have the right to be a goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:08.84,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,She's still clinging to that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:11.18,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,That's okay. I haven't given it\Nany thought, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:13.14,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,You should be apologetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:15.51,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,Really, don't get so down about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.51,0:06:16.19,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Yui-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:19.38,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,I think this is a time when you \Nshould still be unsure of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:22.34,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,To be honest, I don't have \Nall the answers myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:28.70,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,After all, tomorrow exists because of today \Nand today exists because of tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:31.66,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,That's just like Yui-san! \NWhat a way with words!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:33.62,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,I don't think it really meant anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:35.72,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,What's your short-term goal, Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:37.62,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:41.92,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,I have a lot of homework at the moment, \Nso I feel like I need to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:43.41,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:45.05,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,What's your short-term goal, Rin-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:49.33,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,I guess convincing Hina-chan \Nto let me copy her homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.71,0:06:51.43,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,That's nothing to laugh about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:52.44,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,How about you, Kanon-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.44,0:06:54.15,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,My short-term goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:57.26,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,I'm perfect other than being short,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.26,0:06:59.91,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,so if I grow taller, I might as well be a goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:01.88,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,I'm tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:07.37,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,I do gymnastics, so I don't \Nwant to grow any taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:09.49,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,If anything, I wish I were \Nyour height, Kanon-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:11.79,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,I think we're about the same height, Yui-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.79,0:07:14.34,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,That's right! You want to be me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.34,0:07:16.41,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,She didn't say she wanted \Nto be you, Kanon-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:16.91,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:18.29,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:19.16,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:20.32,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,By the way, Koharun,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.32,0:07:23.33,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,you seemed envious earlier when you \Nwere looking at Hiina-senpai's chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:28.23,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,N-No, I wasn't particularly envious,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:33.30,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,but I wish I could experience \Nbeing as big as Hiina-senpai once!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:34.64,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,But the person voicing her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:35.64,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:40.72,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Just watch me after this is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.14,0:07:46.19,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Tomomi-san, is there something \Nyou work hard at?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:49.65,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,I would say... polishing my turret.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:53.53,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Tur... nip? That's very family-oriented of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:54.52,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:58.44,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Tomomi-san, what do you do at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:08:00.04,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,I can't imagine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:04.85,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,I polish my rifle. It's an AK-47.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:08.96,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,It's very reliable, so it may not be necessary \Nto be so careful with it, but I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:11.72,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,AK... Idols?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:16.18,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,It's been around for about 60 years, \Nbut it is my eternal idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:19.54,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,60?! That's a really old idol!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:22.94,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,By the way, what's your \Nshort-term goal, Yui-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:24.68,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,That'd have to be my club!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.68,0:08:26.11,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,I have to do my best with gymnastics!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:29.08,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Huh? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.08,0:08:33.32,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,It says, "Okay, try thinking \Nof a new gymnastics club."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:36.50,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,That must mean apparatus gymnastics.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:38.05,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:39.46,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Me! I've got one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:42.66,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Okay, let's start with Kanon-chan's \N"new gymnastics club."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:47.00,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,The moment you nail your landing, \Nthe floor opens up and you fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:49.09,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,I think I've seen that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:49.84,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:50.78,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,That's in bad taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:53.13,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Don't say that! It's not bad taste...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:53.13,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:57.37,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,That's, like... too nitpicky for a gymnastics club?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.58,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,I've heard of something like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:08:59.56,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Wait. Stop it, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:00.85,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Next! Let's move on. Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:01.74,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:02.90,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Okay, next...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:04.10,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:07.65,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Then Tomomi-chan's "new gymnastics club"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:08.50,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,I'm Hina!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:09.18,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:10.36,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Hina-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:13.24,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Hina-chan's "new gymnastics club"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:16.78,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Um, you do radio calisthenics flawlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.17,0:09:19.24,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,That'd be tough in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:22.40,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,And... And while using the apparatus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:24.48,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Um, what is it again? The pommel horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:26.79,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,You do radio calisthenics while standing on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:28.50,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:30.70,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,You'd lose your balance, \Nhorsing around on a pommel horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:32.66,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Um, how would... \NHow would you do this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.66,0:09:34.13,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,How would you do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:35.05,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,W-Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:35.05,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,This kind of stretch...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:35.78,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:36.22,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Rin-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:39.36,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,No, Tomomi-san said, \N"How would you do this one?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.36,0:09:41.32,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Did I say something funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.32,0:09:42.47,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Rin-chan did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:43.51,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,Say it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.51,0:09:44.77,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Would you repeat what you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:50.99,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Y-You'd lose your balance on the pommel \Nhorse... if you're horsing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:54.65,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you went there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:56.65,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Well... I felt compelled to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:57.94,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Okay, back on topic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.94,0:10:00.81,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,I'm responsible for this awkwardness, but, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.81,0:10:04.35,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Tomomi-san, did you think of something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:05.89,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,That's me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:08.45,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Would you stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.45,0:10:10.08,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Did you think of something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:13.54,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Would you stop looking at me \Nand saying "Tomomi"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.54,0:10:15.09,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,That's a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:16.17,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Did you think of something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:17.88,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,I'm Tomomi. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:20.09,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Oh, I know. Zdravstvujte.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:23.13,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,She's making fun of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:23.13,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Zdravstvujte...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:26.58,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,She's making fun of me, but I've got one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.58,0:10:28.85,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Okay, Tomomi-san's "new gymnastics club"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.51,0:10:32.50,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,The equipment rises up against humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:35.11,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Like, mech-rings versus humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:36.06,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Huh? "Versus"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:39.36,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,The rings, like, get bigger and bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:40.58,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,They get bigger?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.58,0:10:41.41,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They get huge...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:42.45,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:46.52,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,...and then they take the \Nentire student body away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:50.77,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,And then, um, they train them \Nall on some distant planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.77,0:10:54.90,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,make them their allies, and then return to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:53.12,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,They're guinea pigs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:56.33,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,That's large-scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:56.45,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,That turned into a grand story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.45,0:10:59.40,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,So eventually, it's humans \Ncompeting against humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:00.34,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:01.79,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,I see. Because they're trained on another planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.11,0:11:03.51,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,They compete against the trained humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:05.24,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,They also fight the rings along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:06.12,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,"Along the way" now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:08.77,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Wow! You've got a whole story there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:08.15,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,It's sci-fi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.74,0:11:15.88,Main Dialogue,Mob,0,0,0,,Hey, Grandmob, what kind of anime \Nis {\i1}Tesagure! Bukatsumono{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:18.75,Main Dialogue,Mobuba,0,0,0,,First, watch this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:23.87,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Koharun, you look kind of down today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:27.64,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Yes, actually, I didn't get \Nmuch sleep last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.64,0:11:32.98,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,I know! Koharun, you're wearing \Nworn-out panties, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:36.43,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,You're wearing worn-out panties?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:38.80,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Yua-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:42.40,Main Dialogue,Mob,0,0,0,,It's an anime about the girls in the Tesaguri Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:43.70,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:45.80,Main Dialogue,Mob,0,0,0,,This part is called the pre-title.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:50.57,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Please don't say it in such a loud voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.57,0:11:54.44,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,There are boys around here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:55.36,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:59.33,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Like that protagonist-type boy over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.33,0:12:03.70,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Oh, come on! It's totally fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:08.53,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,For some reason, when the protagonist is a boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.53,0:12:12.97,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,even when girls say important things,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:21.12,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,he never seems to hear a thing \Ngirls say, so I believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.12,0:12:23.08,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,It's no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:26.01,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:30.60,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Koharun said she's wearing \Nworn-out panties today!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:33.84,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,She said threads are showing everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:35.16,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Hey, Yua-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.16,0:12:39.02,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,On top of that, she said that \Nwhen she imagines you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:43.48,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,playing "helping hands" with another boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.48,0:12:48.45,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,she gets all excited by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:50.85,Main Dialogue,Boy,0,0,0,,Huh? Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:51.98,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,There, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:54.26,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,What?! How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.26,0:12:56.49,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,It's strange, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.49,0:13:00.44,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Please stop playing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.99,0:13:06.27,From Sign,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}From episode 11 of anime {\i1}Tesagure! Bukatsumono{\i0} \N"Worn-out Panties Pre-title" (in E Major)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:12.82,Main Dialogue,Mob,0,0,0,,After the pre-title, the members \Nassemble in a convenient club room
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:15.84,Main Dialogue,Mob,0,0,0,,and talk about other clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:20.83,Main Dialogue,Mob,0,0,0,,Really? That sounds like \Nyour typical slice-of-life thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:27.78,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Shall we talk about the tennis club today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:34.00,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Good idea! What's your \Nimage of the tennis club?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:35.58,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Graceful flirts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:42.60,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,What?! I can't tell if you're praising \Nthem or insulting them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:49.80,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Well, certainly, it is a sport \Nthat's gentlemanly and elegant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:53.39,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,And the girls in the club
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:57.06,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,wear those cute uniforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:14:03.13,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,I bet lots of them get into \Nthe club just because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:04.71,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.71,0:14:06.13,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Elegant flirts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:08.31,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,How to score points.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:09.86,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Elegant flirts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:11.91,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Eccentric.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:13.34,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Elegant flirts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:15.43,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,E-mail address.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.43,0:14:16.92,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Elegant flirts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:19.17,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Wimbledon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:23.17,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,When you receive, spin your racket.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:23.92,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Elegant flirts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:26.15,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Like playing the guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:27.47,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Elegant flirts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:29.81,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Telling a one-shot joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.81,0:14:31.10,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Elegant flirts, elegant flirts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:33.24,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Group photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.24,0:14:34.94,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Elegant flirts, elegant flirts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:36.68,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Wrap your racket in a spiral shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:41.79,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,When they pick up the ball, \Nthey scoop it up with the racket.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.33,0:14:45.31,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,{\a6}If you miss a shot, they'll yell at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:49.25,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Anyway, the tennis club is full \Nof elegant flirts to the max!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.25,0:14:54.17,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Aoi-senpai, are you in \Nsome weird mode right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:14:55.76,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Elegant flirts max!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:58.28,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Elegant flirts max!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:02.30,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Elegant flirts max!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:05.95,From Sign,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}From episode 8 of anime {\i1}Tesagure! Bukatsumono{\i0} \N"Things That Happen in the Tennis Club" (in E flat Major)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:10.10,Main Dialogue,Mob,0,0,0,,After talking about the club,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:13.89,Main Dialogue,Mob,0,0,0,,they imagine what the club \Nwould be like if it were anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:16.52,Main Dialogue,Mob,0,0,0,,Take a look at the newspaper club episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.01,0:15:20.86,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,The protagonist is a high school boy with a
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.86,0:15:24.83,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,talented newspaper reporter for a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.20,0:15:30.60,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,The supporting character is his \Nchildhood friend who's a busybody,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:34.51,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,and also a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.84,0:15:38.72,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Even though he's got a nose \Nfor scoops and crimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:43.61,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,he's a dullard when it comes to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:48.64,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Jeez! When is he going to figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.64,0:15:56.56,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,the feelings that I have for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.56,0:15:59.53,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Sheesh! He makes me so mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.53,0:16:02.39,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,I'm gonna tell him myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:11.32,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,The members of the newspaper club are \Nalways driven to solve the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:13.77,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Hey, let's not report this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.77,0:16:14.77,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:17.02,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,It's our duty to report the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.02,0:16:22.25,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,I don't think it always is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:26.49,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Wow! We've got a whole
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.49,0:16:30.88,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,story here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:35.54,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,So what happens to the father in the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.54,0:16:38.53,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:42.01,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Because it was all a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:44.61,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Th-That's the punchline?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:48.41,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,It was all the father's dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:53.18,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Not even the protagonist's dream, \Nbut the protagonist's father's?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.18,0:16:55.03,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,That's new!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:06.79,From Sign,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}From episode 7 of anime {\i1}Tesagure! Bukatsumono{\i0}\N"Things That Would Happen in a Newspaper Club Anime" (in E Major)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:12.29,Main Dialogue,Mob,0,0,0,,Many things happen during a long life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.29,0:17:17.78,Main Dialogue,Mob,0,0,0,,It was a tragic accident \Nthat we must never forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:20.25,Main Dialogue,Mob,0,0,0,,What? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:26.17,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Well, now that we've shared our images
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:31.11,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,of the art club,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:37.35,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,let's come up with a new art club.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:38.76,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Go ahead, Hiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:45.79,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to draw pictures,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:52.96,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,but I have no artistic talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:58.18,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,I want to draw, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:17:59.41,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Butt?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:00.85,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:05.08,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,I don't mean "butt" as in "ass," but "but,"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.08,0:18:08.86,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,like "but the kid is absent today."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.86,0:18:16.13,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,You really thought I imagined the \Nstudents drawing their rear ends?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:16.94,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Scratch, scratch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.94,0:18:23.23,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,That's something a professional \Nrakugo storyteller would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.23,0:18:23.98,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Rakugo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.98,0:18:24.85,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Rock a goat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:32.79,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,This is NTV, so at least watch {\i1}Shoten{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.79,0:18:36.51,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,You guys are taking it too easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:45.61,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,At least watch {\i1}Shoten{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:50.03,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,I wanna go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.03,0:18:53.44,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,I didn't think it was gonna end \Non a vulgar note like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:55.18,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,It's the pun version!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.18,0:18:57.65,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,There sure were a lot of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:05.91,From Sign,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}From episode 4 of anime {\i1}Tesagure! Bukatsumono{\i0}\N"The Sad Last Act ~Taking It Too Easy~" (in G Minor)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:10.06,Main Dialogue,Mob,0,0,0,,Of course, they're not all sad stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:13.92,Main Dialogue,Mob,0,0,0,,Sometimes very good things \Nhappen that make everyone smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:22.59,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,I welcome all of your attacking tackles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:24.34,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:25.71,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Come on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.71,0:19:28.82,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,I call it a "hugby."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.82,0:19:30.60,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,That sounds too hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:34.59,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,They're all rather fruity guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:38.65,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,so they go after each other for hugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.68,0:19:38.65,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Oh, what a handsome guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:45.30,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,If they're lucky, they might \Ncatch a different kind of ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:46.64,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Two balls! Two balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:47.62,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Grab hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:51.54,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,We do silly stuff like this all the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:55.38,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,But we have a good reason for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:19:58.30,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,There's no single thing that we {\i1}have{\i0} to do or be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:03.14,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,So why don't you join us to look for \Nwhatever it is that suits you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:07.24,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,If you accept yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:11.13,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,other people will accept you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.13,0:20:14.75,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,We'll make a place for you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.75,0:20:18.96,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,in this place right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:23.45,Main Dialogue,All,0,0,0,,It's more important who you spend time with
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:27.43,Main Dialogue,All,0,0,0,,than what you spend time doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:30.92,Main Dialogue,All,0,0,0,,There's no need to hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.92,0:20:35.49,Main Dialogue,All,0,0,0,,Let's grow together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:41.24,Main Dialogue,Mob,0,0,0,,Grandmob, I think I understand a little\Nmore about {\i1}Tesagure! Bukatsumono {\i0}now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:44.20,Main Dialogue,Mob,0,0,0,,They still have a long way to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:48.23,Main Dialogue,Mob,0,0,0,,but I hope we can grow along with them.
