Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:34.45,Main Dialogue,Mob,0,0,0,,Okay, question. What's an \Nunusual play in pro baseball?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.45,0:22:36.04,Main Dialogue,Mob,0,0,0,,Uno's heading incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.04,0:22:38.92,Main Dialogue,Mob,0,0,0,,Okay, question. What's a \Nfamous baseball saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.92,0:22:42.00,Main Dialogue,Mob,0,0,0,,Coach Nagashima Shigeo's \N"Swing with the bat and hit the ball!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.00,0:22:45.42,Main Dialogue,Mob,0,0,0,,Okay, question. What is \NKawasaki Stadium famous for?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:48.13,Main Dialogue,Mob,0,0,0,,Couples kissing in the bleachers \Nduring the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.13,0:22:50.97,Main Dialogue,Mob,0,0,0,,You're all perfectly in sync today, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.97,0:22:52.55,Main Dialogue,Mob,0,0,0,,All right, last question!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.55,0:22:55.06,Main Dialogue,Mob,0,0,0,,What are the highlights of the \N{\i1}Tesagure! Bukatsumono{\i0} spin-off?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.06,0:22:57.23,Main Dialogue Top,Mob,0,0,0,,Alligators!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.06,0:22:57.23,Main Dialogue Top,Mob,0,0,0,,Knee-high socks!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.06,0:22:57.23,Main Dialogue,Mob,0,0,0,,Softshell turtle!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.06,0:22:57.23,Main Dialogue,Mob,0,0,0,,The ice cream is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.23,0:22:59.30,Main Dialogue,Mob,0,0,0,,Why aren't you in sync on this one?!
